🧠 Kidney Chronic Disease Prediction
📝 Introduction
This project focuses on predicting Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD) using machine learning techniques. By analyzing patient data, the models aim to assist in early detection and diagnosis of CKD, potentially improving patient outcomes through timely intervention.

